Young, Respondent, v. Metropolitan El. R. Co. et al.. Appellants. (Common Pleas of New York City and County, General Term. November, 1889.) Appeal from special term.

Argued before Larremore, C. J., and Bookstaver, J.

Davies & Rapallo, for appellants. Sackett & Bennett, for respondent.

No opinion. Judgment affirmed, with costs.
